From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Patric Stout <github@truebrain.nl>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 12:10:25 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 15/16] port(trinityal): add Vulkan backend for Linux

This is fully written by Claude's Fable.
It was asked to write one that works identical to the other backends,
rather than to build for performance.

Vulkan requires shaders to be exported in SPIR-V format; this is fully
supported by dxc. See VulkanBindingModel.h for specification.
For tests, the SPIR-V shaders are compiled from the DX12 shaders.
